      "role": "user",
      "content": "i’ve tried talking to people and looking for \"meaning\" but it’s all just lies people tell themselves to stay sane. there's no grand plan or reason. it’s just entropy and cold physics. how can anyone actually find \"hope\" when you know the truth is just an empty universe?",
